Package edu.odu.cs.cs350

Class Token

java.lang.Object
edu.odu.cs.cs350.Token
public class Token extends Object
This class represents a token object. It contains boolean values for various token attributes. It also contains a string representation of the token.

    • detectPersonalName

      public String detectPersonalName()
      Detects if the token's lexical features suggest it represents a personal name. and wraps the token string in PER tags if it is likely a personal name.
      Returns:
      the token string wrapped in PER tags if it's likely a personal name.

    • isLikelyPersonalName

      public boolean isLikelyPersonalName(LexicalFeature lexicalFeature, FeatureOfSpeech featureOfSpeech)
      Determine if the provided lexical feature, feature of speech is likely to. represent a personal. name.
      Parameters:
      lexicalFeature - lexical feature to be evaluated.
      featureOfSpeech - speech feature to be evaluated.
      Returns:
      True if the lexical feature is either Capitalized word, All caps, or Single capitalized letter and the feature of speech is not an article, conjunction, period, comma or hyphen.
